{"tid":2261793,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"法國自己啲屋企人真係痴鳩線","createTime":"2020-10-28T14:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T15:22:09.000Z","uid":90316,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ec311e9ecaf127d483b3040e10ef30132fe556aa","tid":2261793,"uid":90316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T14:53:59.000Z","msg":"自己一邊係度話宜家個市道好撚差 又炒好多人 又好多人失業又盛 但果頭又搏撚哂老命吹鳩我搵工 好似畀少幾個月家用 佢哋會少忽肉咁 cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大佬呀 我腥成幾百封cv都冇人候 你估我想架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都想搵份濕鳩文員仔做住先 但又要簽contract 到時見到第份正職又要賠遺約金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係唔係你班廢老幫我畀先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到我話想搵份熊貓長頸鹿打住先 貪佢啲時間够鬆動 可以隨時去interview 屌你又話咁多錢咁辛苦供你讀書 你走去同我送外賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係哭撚左 你想我點撚樣呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到前幾日我叫佢開戶去抽ibond轉手賺幾百 又話我冇鳩用 要借佢啲錢去賺錢 又話我要用自己啲錢先用得光明正大咁又講到我仙人跳咁呃佢啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一 隻ibond你都有份抽 即係抽到你都有錢賺 仲要係接近0風險必賺咁滯 <br />\n<br />\n第二 我唔叫你抽呀 你識閪咩 一日到黑淨係睇撚到住三色電視 又屌侵又黑3人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第三 仲屈鳩我政府果一萬蚊 要我買電腦畀細妹 話咩以前我買畀你 宜家到你買返畀個細嘅咁 如果唔畀你屈鳩我啲錢 我駛撚同你借錢 買多幾手添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要成日提撚住咩 我宜家供够你讀書 宜家到你供反個細嘅咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大老呀 你養唔掂就咪撚生啦 養唔到又要塞個波畀人 好似我老馮欠撚左佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打撚完一大篇 純粹想呻下 屌 聽日又死頂畀廢老屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a39fc5ffdc58aab0a1999cb3295c72fa0ad423","tid":2261793,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T14:55:33.000Z","msg":"生你出黎就係要你畀家用架啦"},{"pid":"02da204cd76d51c8d913d07df979772960118863","tid":2261793,"uid":90316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T14:56:14.000Z","msg":"仲要頭先腥埋個勞工處招聘會廣告嚟 屌撚你咩 入面全部保安樓面 我肯做呀 又畀你屌我 咁高學歷做啲閪工 嘥晒啲錢我供你讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face